Content: I love my glasses! Getting my frames and glasses from my eye doctor would take several weeks before, not to mention finding time during the week where my schedule and the optical tech's schedule would line up so I could go and get my new glasses was always the biggest hassle. I hated the process and I hated the wait (my optometrist office isn't the greatest but that's another review for another website) and I really wanted to find something faster, easier, and with a wider variety of frames that would take my insurance and my search brought me here! I spent an hour or so on this website, found these glasses, tried them on and ordered them and within the day they were shipped and within the week I had them. They fit perfectly and everything! Its weird and scary at first ordering your glasses online and I know I had a lot of worries and questions but honestly I would (and very likely will) continue to get my glasses this way since its so convenient and hassle free!
